---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="CLE Module 2: AI Risk &amp; Candor | Generative AI Use Training"
  description="CLE training module covering AI risk and the duty of candor to the tribunal when using generative AI in legal practice. Developed by Christian Kameir."
>
  <article class="cle-sample">
    <div class="container--wide">

      <!-- ── Header ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <header class="cle-sample__header">
        <p class="label">CLE Course — Module 2</p>
        <h1 class="cle-sample__title">AI Risk &amp; Candor</h1>
        <p class="cle-sample__intro">
          How generative AI fails — and what those failure modes mean for
          an attorney's duty of candor to the tribunal. Part of the
          <em>Generative AI Use Mandatory Training</em> CLE course.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- ── Video ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="cle-sample__video">
        <div class="cle-sample__embed-wrapper">
          <iframe
            src="https://app.heygen.com/embeds/4b71cf8f970a4cdf98eef24505fa1fdb"
            title="Module 2 - AI Risk &amp; Candor"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="encrypted-media; fullscreen;"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── About ───────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="cle-sample__section">
        <p class="cle-sample__section-label">About this module</p>
        <p class="cle-sample__body">
          This module catalogs the seven most consequential AI failure modes attorneys
          encounter in practice — from hallucination and prompt injection to context-window
          truncation and overconfidence signaling — and maps each directly to Model Rules
          3.1 and 3.3. Attorneys leave with a concrete checklist for pre-filing AI output
          review.
        </p>
        <p class="cle-sample__body">
          Developed by Christian Kameir, whose practice spans technology law, venture
          finance, and AI policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="rule" />

      <!-- ── CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
      <section class="cle-sample__cta">
        <p class="cle-sample__cta-text">
          Interested in licensing the full course for your firm or bar association?
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Get in touch</a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
.cle-sample__header {
  padding-top: 4rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.cle-sample__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.cle-sample__intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

.cle-sample__video {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-l);
}

.cle-sample__embed-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  background: var(--surface, #f4f4f4);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.cle-sample__embed-wrapper iframe {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  border: none;
}

.cle-sample__section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-l);
  padding-block: var(--space-m);
}

.cle-sample__section-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.cle-sample__body {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text);
  max-width: 640px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.cle-sample__cta {
  padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.cle-sample__cta-text {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  max-width: 520px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
}
</style>
